Package: covSummary
Type: Package
Title: R Package to summarise .cov files
Description: Function(s) to calculate average methylation, and additional QC metrics, from coverage (.cov) files generated by bismark. This function will efficiently loop through all .cov files in a specified directory, providing a single summary table.
Version: 1.0
